.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, electrician, nurse, paramedic
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, family, superhero
1. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the nurse##8
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
3. the electrician is on the right of the bartender##1
4. the electrician is in an even position##4
5. the paramedic is on the far left or far right##3
6. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
7. the paramedic is the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | bartender | electrician | nurse     | paramedic |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | superhero   | adventure | family    |

