.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, disco, metal, rock
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the fan of disco##1
4. the fan of rock is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
5. the fan of blues is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | disco         | rock   | blues    |
| Sport         | parkour | weightlifting | soccer | lacrosse |

