.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, kiwi, lettuce, pineapple
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, indie, pop
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the person eating cauliflower##5
3. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
5. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
6. the person eating pineapple is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
7. the person eating pineapple is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | pineapple | cauliflower | kiwi  | lettuce |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | pop         | indie | ambient |

