.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, indie, pop
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, bus, taxi, trike
1. the fan of classical is between the fan of pop and the person driving the boat##2
2. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
4. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
5. the person driving the bus is the person driving the bus##1
6. the fan of indie is not the person driving the taxi##6
7. the fan of pop is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
8. the person driving the boat is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | classical | indie | dubstep |
| Transport     | trike | bus       | boat  | taxi    |

