1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##8
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person drinking fanta##7
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | fanta         | juice    | cola       |
| Sport      | handball | skateboarding | biathlon | ice-hockey |

