.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, papaya, watermelon, zucchini
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, family, superhero
 1. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching family movies##5
 2. the person eating zucchini is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
 3. the person eating grapefruit is the person watching family movies##1
 4. the person watching family movies is not to the right of the person watching crime movies##8
 5. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 6. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 7. the person watching crime movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the person watching family movies##8
 9. the person watching crime movies is not to the left of the person eating grapefruit##8
10. the person eating papaya is not to the left of the person watching adventure movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | papaya    | watermelon | grapefruit | zucchini |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | superhero  | family     | crime    |

