The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, drawing, reading, video-games
1. the person eating grapefruit is the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is not to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person eating peas##1
5. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
6. the person eating avocado is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person eating peas##2
7. the person eating grapefruit is in an even position##4

