.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, rabbit, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, jet-ski, trike
1. the owner of the snake is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
2. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the snake##7
4. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
5. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5
6. the person driving the bike is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
7. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | cat  | snake | fish  | rabbit  |
| Transport   | bike | car   | trike | jet-ski |

