.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, hamster, hedgehog
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, subway, van
1. the person driving the jet-ski is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the person driving the van##8
4. the owner of the hamster is the person driving the car##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the car##7
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the van and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | frog    | hedgehog | chinchilla | hamster |
| Transport   | jet-ski | van      | subway     | car     |

